INSTALLATION

1.  Upload all files to your hosting package.  Suggested permissions are 755 except the cache folder which needs 777.
2.  Go to the includes folder and open configuration.php.  Fill out your MySQL database information.  
3.  For PHP Backups to work you will need to go into the phpBackup folder and edit backup.php to have your MySQL database information in it as well
4.  For PHP Backups to be emailed to you, you will need to fill out backup.php to have the proper email account information.  
5.  Restore the SQL database backup `database.zip`.
6.  Default group is 'default', username 'admin', password 'admin'